---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

export const prerender = true;
---

<!-- heading color changes to - text-[#4a505a] -->
<MainLayout>
    <div class="bg-[#30353E] px-8 text-white py-10 2xl:px-56">
        <div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-5">
            <a href="/" class="text-white inline-block">
                <svg
                    class="w-7 h-7"
                    viewBox="0 0 56 56"
                    fill="none"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M28.0003 11.6665L11.667 27.9998M11.667 27.9998L28.0003 44.3332M11.667 27.9998L44.3337 27.9998"
                        stroke="white"
                        stroke-width="4"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
            </a>
            <div class="text-3xl">Terms & Conditions</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="px-12 my-16 text-[#687383] 2xl:px-56">
        <div>Welcome to Ground Lens!</div>
        <br>
        <p>
            By accessing or using our website, you agree to the following Terms
            of Use. Please read these terms carefully to understand your rights
            and obligations.
        </p>
        <br>
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            1. General Use of the Website <br />
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    This website provides infographics, articles, videos, motion
                    graphics, visuals, and designs, and other resources on real
                    estate and various general topics for informational and
                    educational purposes.
                </li>
                <li>
                    The content on this website is not intended as professional
                    advice. Users should seek specific guidance when needed.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            2. Intellectual Property Rights
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    All content available on the Ground Lens website, including
                    but not limited to infographics, articles, images, text,
                    motion graphics, videos, and other materials, is the
                    exclusive property of Ground Lens unless otherwise stated.
                </li>
                <li class="font-medium">
                    You are strictly prohibited from:
                    <ul
                        class="list-[upper-roman] list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 font-normal"
                    >
                        <li>
                            Copying, reproducing, modifying, distributing, or
                            transmitting the content for commercial or public
                            purposes without prior written consent
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Using the content in any manner that misrepresents
                            its original intent or purpose.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li class="font-medium">
                    Permitted Sharing:
                    <br />
                    <span class="font-normal ml-4">
                        We encourage users to share our content responsibly on
                        their personal social media accounts, provided that:
                    </span>
                    <ul
                        class="list-[upper-roman] list-inside ml-8 space-y-1 font-normal"
                    >
                        <li>
                            Proper credit is given to Ground Lens by tagging or
                            linking back to the original website or post
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            The content is not altered, edited, or used out of
                            context
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            The sharing complies with the terms and conditions
                            of the respective social media platform
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Any misuse of our intellectual property, including
                    unauthorized use, reproduction, or distribution, may result
                    in legal action.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            3. Use of Quotes and Third-Party Content
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 list-inside ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    Our website may feature quotes or information from publicly
                    available sources, attributed to their respective authors or
                    publications
                </li>
                <li>
                    References to articles or external information are properly
                    credited
                </li>
                <li>
                    If you believe any content violates copyright or attribution
                    rights, please notify us promptly
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            4. User Conduct <br />
            <p class="ml-4 mt-2">By using this website, you agree not to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 list-inside ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>Use the content for illegal activities or purposes.</li>
                <li>Disrupt the operation or security of the website</li>
                <li>
                    Claim ownership or misrepresent the content shared on the
                    website.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            5. Disclaimer
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 list-inside ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    The content provided is for informational purposes only.
                    While we strive for accuracy, we do not guarantee the
                    completeness or reliability of the information.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Ground Lens is not responsible for any actions or decisions
                    made based on our content.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            6. Third-Party Links
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 list-inside ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    The website may include links to third-party websites for
                    reference or additional information.
                </li>
                <li>
                    We do not endorse or assume responsibility for the content,
                    practices, or policies of these third-party sites.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            7. Content Variation
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 list-inside ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    While the website primarily focuses on real estate-related
                    topics, we may also share infographics and articles on
                    general subjects of interest.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            8. Changes to Terms of Use
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 list-inside ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>
                    Ground Lens reserves the right to update these Terms of Use
                    at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with a
                    revised effective date
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#4a505a]">
            9. Contact Information
            <br />
            <p class="font-normal ml-4">
                For questions or concerns about these Terms of Use, please
                contact us:
            </p>
            <p class="font-normal ml-4">
                Email :
                <a
                    href="mailto:info@groundlens.in"
                    target="_blank"
                    title="mailto:info@groundlens.in"
                >
                    info@groundlens.in
                </a>
            </p>
        </p>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
